偿献血制度。 常巨平建议全国人大常委会对《献血法》以下之部分条款进行修改。其中建议第十条第三款建议修改为：“血站对采集的血液必须进行检测，未经检测或者检测不合格的血液不得向医疗机构提供。不合格血液的利用、监督，由国务院卫生健康行政主管部门另行制定管理办法。” 另外建议第十一条建议修改为：“无偿献血的血液不得买卖，合格的血液必须用于临床；临床使用之外的血液，有关血站、医疗机构不得出售给单采血浆站或者血液制品生产单位，应按有关规定加以有效利用。” 全国人大代表常巨平：建议修改《献血法》部分条款_血液_检测_我国"},"attached_info":"CkAIkLCtoN/tj7UaEAMaCTEwNjA4ODE2NiCDlJuvBjAAOKQFQC1yCTY0NzE0ODQ2MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"3.4 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-3ba4298e70b020a5a5627c0ce7c03b3e_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"46_1710054952.899197","card_id":"Q_647554680","target":{"id":647554680,"title":"网飞版《三体》发布终极预告，有哪些不易察觉的细节？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/647554680","type":"question","created":1709871458,"answer_count":93,"follower_count":154,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[316,851,3269,673479],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"NETFLIX发布科幻剧集《三体》终极中字预告。60年代的中国，一名年轻女性做出了关键决定掀起时空波澜，定档3.21上线播出。 ​"},"attached_info":"CkAIkLCtoN/tj7UaEAMaCTEwNjE3ODMyNyDioqqvBjAAOJoBQC5yCTY0NzU1NDY4MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"热度累计中","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"47_1710054952.900546","card_id":"Q_647734894","target":{"id":647734894,"title":"23-24赛季NBA常规赛雄鹿122：123湖人，拉塞尔44分9助攻绝杀雄鹿，如何评价这场比赛？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/647734894","type":"question","created":1709966579,"answer_count":28,"follower_count":39,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[744,35258,35500,35504,91824],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IkLCtoN/tj7UaEAMaCTEwNjIxODM5NiDzibCvBjAAOCdAL3IJNjQ3NzM0ODk0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=